<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.10">
<l>añcuvaṉ colli yaḻaittiṭa naṅkaikā ḷāyira nāḻi neyyaip</l>
<l>pañciyal mellaṭip piḷḷai kaḷuṇkiṉṟu pākantāṉ vaiyār kaḷē</l>
<l>kañcaṉ kaṭiyaṉ kaṟaveṭṭu nāḷileṉ kaivalat tātu millai</l>
<l>neñcat tiruppaṉa ceytuvait tāynampī yeṉceykē ṉeṉcey kēṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ladies, I’m afraid to shout [at him], saying [anything]!</l>
<l rend="indent">The children with cotton soft feet,</l>
<l>Being able to eat one-thousand measures of ghee, did not leave a bit.</l>
<l>Kaṁsa is evil; tribute is [due] in eight days. There is nothing in my hand.</l>
<l>You do these things to my heart, prince, [and I suffer].</l>
<l rend="indent">What do I do? What do I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
